/char> (cop<char style="add">sa<char style="add">mss</char></char> slav) ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τὸ κράτος καὶ ἡ δόξα </char><char style="ft" closed="false">5 33 81 1175 1243 1448 1611 1739 1852 2344 <char style="it">l</char> 1298 <char style="it">l</char> 1365 syr<char style="add">h</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> arm ⫽ <char style="it">virtus et potestas</char> it<char style="add">h, q</char> vg<char style="add">mss</char></char></note> εἰς τοὺς αἰῶνας<char style="add">♦</char>, ἀμήν.</para>
  <para style="s">Final Greetings</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Διὰ Σιλουανοῦ ὑμῖν τοῦ πιστοῦ ἀδελφοῦ, ὡς λογίζομαι, δι᾽ ὀλίγων ἔγραψα παρακαλῶν καὶ ἐπιμαρτυρῶν ταύτην εἶναι ἀληθῆ χάριν τοῦ θεοῦ εἰς ἣν στῆτε. <verse number="13" style="v" />Ἀσπάζεται ὑμᾶς ἡ ἐν Βαβυλῶνι<note caller="9" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Βαβυλῶνι </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> A B Ψ 5 33 81 307 436 442 642 1175 1243 1448 1611* 1735 1739 1852 2344 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">h, q</char> vg<char style="add">st</char> syr<char style="add">h</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> geo slav Origen Eusebius ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Βαβυλῶνι ἐκκλησία </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ it<char style="add">ar, z</char> vg<char style="add">cl, ww</char> syr<char style="add">p</char> arm eth<char style="add">pp</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Ῥώμῃ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">1611<char style="add">c</char></char></note> συνεκλεκτὴ καὶ Μᾶρκος ὁ υἱός μου. <verse number="14" style="v" />ἀσπάσασθε ἀλλήλους ἐν φιλήματι ἀγάπης<note caller="10" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5.14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἀγάπης </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> ℵ A B Ψ 33 81 307 442 1175 1243 1448 1611 1739 1852 2344 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">h, q</char> syr<char style="add">h</char> cop<char style="add">(sa), bo</char> eth slav geo Cyril-Jerusalem; Cassiodorus ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἁγίῳ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">5 436 642 1735 <char style="it">l</char> 593 <char style="it">l</char> 1298 <char style="it">l</char> 1365 it<char style="add">ar, z</char> vg syr<char style="add">p</char> arm ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἁγίῳ καὶ ἀγάπης </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="it">l</char> 422 (cop<char style="add">bo<char style="add">ms</char></char>)</char></note>. εἰρήνη ὑμῖν πᾶσιν τοῖς ἐν Χριστῷ.<note caller="11" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5.14 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Χριστῷ. </char><char style="ft" closed="false">A B Ψ 2344 it<char style="add">ar, z</char> vg<char style="add">st</char> cop<char style="add">sa<char style="add">ms</char>, bo<char style="add">mss</char></char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Χριστῷ. ἀμήν. </char><char style="ft" closed="false">2492 <char style="it">l</char> 895 <char style="it">l</char> 1365 <char style="it">l</char> 1441 vg<char style="add">ww</char> syr<char style="add">p</char> eth ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">♦ Χριστῷ Ἰησοῦ. </char><char style="ft" closed="false">81 1175 1243 1739* cop<char style="add">sa<char style="add">mss</char>, bo<char style="add">mss</char></char> geo ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Χριστῷ Ἰησοῦ. ἀμήν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ 5 307 436 442 642 1448 1611 1735 1739<char style="add">c</char> 1852 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">h</char> vg<char style="add">cl</char> syr<char style="add">h</char> cop<char style="add">bo<char style="add">mss</char></char> arm slav</char></note><char style="add">♦</char></para>
